text: The 2019 Symetra Tour was a series of professional women's golf tournaments held from March through October 2019 in the United States. The Symetra Tour is the second-tier women's professional golf tour in the United States and is the "official developmental tour" of the LPGA Tour. It was previously known as the Futures Tour. ==Schedule and results== The number in parentheses after winners' names show the player's total number of official money, individual event wins on the
